Name: ROCPAIN: Rock Paper Scissors
About the game: A paper airplane fights against Rock, Paper and Scissors. The ROCPAIN gameplay is inspired on the rock-paper-scissors hand game, and like the original hand game, each enemy only its destroyed with the right shot. A new way to play shooting games that will challenge your skills. Journey through new worlds, win the challenges, unlock achievements and make as many points as you can. 2 Levels 4 Difficulty modes 24 Achievements Leaderboards
